high_descs: Walk to the kitchen sink on your right.
Grab a potato from the sink.
Walk to the microwave on your left.
Put the potato in the microwave, then take it out.
Walk back to the kitchen sink on your right.
Put the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato and replace it.

high_descs: Walk to the right of the counter and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the potato in the sink.
Turn left and look up to face the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn right to face the sink.
Place the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato plus return it to the sink.

high_descs: cook potato in microwave, remove potato from microwave
anns.task_desc: put cooked potato into kitchen sink
